I"14<h2 id="sequelize">Sequelize</h2>

<h3 id="sequelize-cli-설치">Sequelize-cli 설치</h3>

<div class="language-jsx highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nx">npm</span> <span class="nx">install</span> <span class="o">--</span><span class="nx">save</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="nx">dev</span> <span class="nx">sequelize</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="nx">cli</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>위 명령어를 입력해 설치한다.</p>

<h3 id="sequelize-cli-초기세팅">Sequelize-cli 초기세팅</h3>

<div class="language-jsx highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nx">npx</span> <span class="nx">sequelize</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="nx">cli</span> <span class="nx">init</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>위 명령어를 입력하면 config, models, migrations, seeders 폴더가 생성된다.</p>

<p>config에는 처음에 config.json파일로</p>

